latestIgtvVideos.title: Bosco Car Therapy Sessions - Greenlight
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
@hellobosco performing 'Greenlight' - during her #BlueRibbonStudios sessions. 

She'll be taking over @1700naud for both December and January, so stay tuned for more.

latestIgtvVideos.title: ✨
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
If you haven’t been following along - the full ‘Wishful Thinking’ series is here. @kliuwong and @lukepelletier took over @1700naud for the month of November to show their collaborative work, ‘Wishful Thinking.’ Hit the bio link to tour it digitally if you didn’t get a chance to stop by. 

Stay tuned for what @hellobosco is up to at Naud for the month of December as our 4th Artist in Residence. #BlueRibbonStudios

latestIgtvVideos.title: 📺
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We said goodbye to ‘Wishful Thinking’ this weekend and we’re gonna miss having @lukepelletier + @kliuwong around at @1700naud. 

If you missed their show (or haven’t checked it out digitally yet), they made some rad bronzed statues. Instead of leaving you with a photo to say farewell, we’ll leave you with this video. And some insight into how they made those things. Yes, one of them is a boob tube.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Workshop Wednesday w/ Chris Pyrate
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Did you miss our live Q+A with @chrispyrate over on @juxtapozmag’s page last month? Don’t worry about it. We just dropped the recap video on our IGTV.

🚨 MARK YOUR CALENDARS our next Workshop Wednesday is gonna be NEXT WEDNESDAY 11/18 with BOTH @lukepelletier + @kliuwong. We commissioned a piece. If you show up and ask a question, you could win it.

latestIgtvVideos.title: THE GOON SALOON
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
We’re on a whole new level with @wizardofbarge and @crocodile.jackson after they took over @1700naud for the month of October. Like, we’ve now met their moms-level. Goon Saloon was great and all, but this might be the best piece that came out of their stay. Check it out (created with help from @monsterchildren). 

Hit the bio link for the full wrap-up of our second #BlueRibbonStudios Artist-In-Residence.

latestIgtvVideos.caption:

🚨 MARK YOUR CALENDARS our next Workshop Wednesday is gonna be THIS WEDNESDAY 10/21 with @chrispyrate. We commissioned a piece. If you show up and ask a question, you could win it.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Blue Ribbon Studios x Shit Art Club
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Experienced Paradis Welldus with @shitartclub as they took over @1700naud for the month of August. This was made (with some help from our buddies @monsterchildren). Along with a ton of art. 

Hit the bio link for a full wrap-up of our first #BlueRibbonStudios Artist-In-Residence.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Workshop Wednesday w/ Jillian Evelyn
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Did you miss our live Q+A with @jillian_evelyn over on @juxtapozmag’s page last month? It’s cool. We just dropped a recap on our IGTV. Check it out. 

🚨 MARK YOUR CALENDARS our next Workshop Wednesday is gonna be on 9/23 with @freakorico. We commissioned a piece. If you show up and ask a question, you could win it.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Coffee Chipotle Beer Can Chicken
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
STRAIGHT FROM YOUR LOCAL BARTENDER is here. Every week we’re teaming up with service industry members to bring you something new to try 🍻
@jeska_amber got a little creative this week and ditched the cocktail for a Coffee Chipotle Beer Can Chicken. We’ve seen a ton of OG beer can chickens….but haven’t seen anyone using our Hard Coffee. If you try it, give us a tag. The full recipe is via our bio link. #StraightFromYourLocalBartender

latestIgtvVideos.title: Workshop Wednesday - @deladeso x PBR
latestIgtvVideos.caption: We commissioned a piece from our long-time friend @deladeso. Check out how he made it and tune into our IG Live at 6pm PST/9pm EST 4/29/20 for the chance to win the finished piece.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Workshop Wednesday - @gaijinarts x PBR
latestIgtvVideos.caption: We commissioned our 2018 Art Can Winner, Gaijin to create a custom piece for us. Check out how he made it and tune into our IG Live at 6pm PST 4/15/20 for the chance to win the finished piece.

latestIgtvVideos.title: @yaicecream Studio Tour
latestIgtvVideos.caption: We commissioned Yai to put together a piece for our Workshop Wednesdays and she also invited us in for a tour of her studio! Check it out + a brief explanation of the process she took to create our commissioned piece. Tune into our IG Live at 6pm PST 4/8/20 for the chance to win it.

latestPosts.caption:
He’s been drinking PBR longer than most of us have been alive and he just turned 100. So we celebrated the only way that felt right: flew to his hometown in Ohio and cracked open a few cold ones with him!
⁠
A WWII veteran, lifelong Pabst fan, and all-around legend.⁠ Cheers to a century of good taste and an even greater life. From the Pabst family to you, Michael. 🍻
